      <title>以色列最高法院冻结神学院经费，令政府不安</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/israel-s-top-court-freezes-seminary-funding-rattling-government</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列最高法院下令政府从下周开始冻结数百所宗教神学院的资金，这对依赖极端正统政党的总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡的执政联盟来说是一个意外打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/israel-s-top-court-freezes-seminary-funding-rattling-government</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 19:33:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>葡萄牙新总理任命萨尔门托为财政部长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/portugal-s-new-premier-picks-sarmento-as-finance-minister</link>
      <description><![CDATA[葡萄牙即将上任的总理任命若阿金·米兰达·萨门托为财政部长，让他负责政府的财政政策，该政府没有获得多数席位，无法确保预算获得批准。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/portugal-s-new-premier-picks-sarmento-as-finance-minister</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 18:48:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>近东救济工程处的资助抵制如何威胁加沙的援助生命线</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/how-the-unrwa-funding-boycott-threatens-gaza-s-aid-lifeline</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在以色列指控 13 名工作人员直接参与 10 月 7 日造成约 1,200 人死亡的哈马斯袭击事件后，美国、德国和日本等十几个国家暂停了向支持巴勒斯坦难民的联合国机构提供资金。以色列长期以来一直指责联合国近东救济工程处（UNRWA）为统治加沙地带并被美国和欧盟认定为恐怖组织的哈马斯提供掩护。美国已暂停向近东救济工程处提供资金 b]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/how-the-unrwa-funding-boycott-threatens-gaza-s-aid-lifeline</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 18:04:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>甲骨文因招标而面临南非政府黑名单</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/oracle-faces-blacklisting-by-south-african-government-over-tender</link>
      <description><![CDATA[为打击腐败和滥用公共资金而设立的南非特别调查组要求国家财政部禁止甲骨文公司与政府开展业务，因为甲骨文公司称其招标存在缺陷。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/oracle-faces-blacklisting-by-south-african-government-over-tender</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 18:00:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>立法者敦促联邦贸易委员会执行罗斯福时代针对杂货价格偏差的法律</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/ftc-is-urged-to-enforce-antitrust-law-over-grocery-price-discrimination</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一群立法者敦促美国联邦贸易委员会在发现亚马逊和沃尔玛等大型零售商在 Covid-19 大流行期间增加利润并保持高价格后，应该执行一项很少使用的反垄断法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/ftc-is-urged-to-enforce-antitrust-law-over-grocery-price-discrimination</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 18:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢拉推动增长，巴西寻求房地产市场提振</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/brazil-seeks-real-estate-market-boost-amid-pressure-to-grow</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦推动经济增长的压力下，巴西正在准备采取措施提振该国的房地产市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/brazil-seeks-real-estate-market-boost-amid-pressure-to-grow</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 17:58:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德克萨斯州采取措施终止利润丰厚的休斯顿收费公路合同</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/texas-takes-step-to-terminate-lucrative-houston-tollway-contract</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德克萨斯州监管机构采取措施终止 Actividades de Construccion y Servicios SA 持有的 52 年收费公路特许经营权，并恢复对该州的控制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/texas-takes-step-to-terminate-lucrative-houston-tollway-contract</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 17:45:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>耶伦被要求调查一家弹药制造商的销售问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/yellen-asked-to-probe-security-issues-in-ammunition-maker-s-sale</link>
      <description><![CDATA[众议院国土安全委员会成员、众议员克莱·希金斯 (Clay Higgins) 要求财政部长珍妮特·耶伦 (Janet Yellen) 在向捷克共和国一家公司出售美国弹药制造商的提议中“彻底审查国家安全问题”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/yellen-asked-to-probe-security-issues-in-ammunition-maker-s-sale</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马杜罗正在测试拜登公平选举协议的极限</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/maduro-tests-limits-of-biden-administration-s-fair-election-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[委内瑞拉总统尼古拉斯·马杜罗公然无视他对自由公正选举的承诺，哥伦比亚和巴西的盟友公开谴责他镇压反对派。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/maduro-tests-limits-of-biden-administration-s-fair-election-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>里约热内卢在狂欢节前几天宣布登革热卫生紧急状态</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-02-05/rio-de-janeiro-has-declared-a-dengue-health-emergency-days-before-carnival-is-due-to-start</link>
      <description><![CDATA[里约热内卢（美联社）——里约热内卢周一宣布，由于爆发蚊媒登革热，该市宣布进入公共卫生紧急状态，就在巴西各地狂欢节庆祝活动开始前几天。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-02-05/rio-de-janeiro-has-declared-a-dengue-health-emergency-days-before-carnival-is-due-to-start</guid>
